secure_file_priv
By default, this variable is empty. If set to the name of a           directory, it limits the effect of the           LOAD_FILE() function and the           LOAD DATA and           SELECT ... INTO           OUTFILE statements to work only with files in that           directory.  This option limits the effect of the           LOAD_FILE() function and the           LOAD DATA and           SELECT ... INTO           OUTFILE statements to work only with files in the           specified directory. 